prompts.frontCover: A charming and minimalist 2D illustration of a birthday beach scene, featuring cartoon versions of Lao Lao (from photo, on left) and Jordan (from photo, on right). The background is a clean, off-white with a simple, elegant wave line in light blue representing the ocean and a soft beige shape for the sand. Lao Lao is laughing joyfully as two tiny, stylized cartoon dogs, one resembling a fluffy Pomeranian and the other a small terrier mix, are playfully trying to pull a birthday present out of her hands with their teeth. She's wearing a casual light blue sweatshirt. Jordan stands beside her, smiling and holding a giant, comically oversized birthday cake with a single lit candle, looking amused by the dogs' antics. In the center of the card, floating above the scene in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao". The overall style is clean, modern, and flat, with a lighthearted and humorous feel.
